                <head>
                    <hi rend="italic">Editorial Note</hi>
                </head>
                <p>For documentation on the views of the United States with respect to a possible
                    Franco-Polish treaty of alliance, see telegrams 2737, May 14, from London, and
                    1847, May 21, to Paris, included in the compilation on concern of the United
                    States with political and economic developments in France, in <ref
                        target="frus1947v03">Volume III</ref>.</p>
            </div>
